### Blue Snow

- why do glaciers have what seems to be blue ice?
- is there such a phenomena as blue snow?
- why do New York people tell stories about "yellow snow"?

### Extrasolar snow

- Consider an earth-like planet exits in orbit around a hot blue star.
  - would blue snow exist on such a planet, if it had oceans and a humid atmosphere?
- Consider a rocky and watery planet orbiting a white dwarf.
  - could blue glacial ice exist on such a planet, if orbiting at the outer fringes of the habitable zone?

